headline: FactSet to Participate in the Bernstein 41st Annual Strategic Decisions Conference
summary: NORWALK, Conn., May 22, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- FactSet (NYSE: FDS | NASDAQ: FDS), a global financial digital platform and enterprise solutions provider, today announced that Chief Executive Officer Phil Snow will participate in a fireside chat at the Bernstein 41st Annual Strategic Decisions Conference in New York on Thursday, May 29, 2025, at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time. To access the live webcast, please visit the event page. By the end of the day, an audio replay of the webcast will be available
